#Lyrics
[Antiphon I] The Lord is God; come, let us adore Him. [Antiphon II] Come, let us worship and bow down; let us kneel before the Lord our Maker. [Antiphon III] Christ the Lord is born today; come, let us worship Him.  [Venite — Psalm 95] Oh come, let us sing to the Lord...

